OL,3,CKurds 'should not be treated as US
OL,4,Ccontractors' amid Iran war
OL,6,FArmy bases are a dangerous place to be
OL,7,Fin Northern Iraq right now, but we
OL,8,Fwere invited to speak to the head of
OL,9,FKurdistan's intelligence forces, so we
OL,10,Ftravelled in an armed convoy to meet
OL,11,Fhim at a classified location.
OL,13,FIf the Kurds were to be drawn into
OL,14,Fthis war with Iran it would be the
OL,15,Ftroops we saw training that would
OL,16,Fcross the border into Iran, to join
OL,17,Fthe fight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
