OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773529872
OL,3,CKurds 'should not be treated as US
OL,4,Ccontractors' amid Iran war
OL,6,FWe watched them conducting an exercise
OL,7,Fto capture an enemy compound. The
OL,8,Fbattle-hardened Kurdish forces have
OL,9,Fproved worthy allies of the United
OL,10,FStates in the past, but they are wary
OL,11,Fof ground conflict in Iran.
OL,13,FIt was the Kurds who helped the US
OL,14,Fdefeat Isis in Iraq and Syria.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
