OL,3,CKurds 'should not be treated as US
OL,4,Ccontractors' amid Iran war
OL,6,FThe Kurds are among the largest
OL,7,Fstateless ethnic groups in the world,
OL,8,Fwith roughly thirty million living as
OL,9,Fminorities in Turkey, Iraq, Iran and
OL,10,FSyria.
OL,12,FThere are armed Kurdish groups inside
OL,13,FIran, organisations and secret cells
OL,14,Fthat could revolt against the Islamic
OL,15,Frepublic if it shows signs of toppling.
OL,17,FAt the start of the war, US President
OL,18,FDonald Trump appeared to suggest it
OL,19,Fcould be Iraqi Kurdish forces that led
OL,20,Fa ground invasion, before backtracking
OL,21,Fon those comments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
