PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773529872
OL,3,CKurds 'should not be treated as US
OL,4,Ccontractors' amid Iran war
OL,6,FAzhi Ameen, the Kurdish intelligence
OL,7,Fboss we met with, said that they
OL,8,Fshould not be treated as American
OL,9,Fcontractors.
OL,11,F"We never make our decisions depending
OL,12,Fon the policies of others; our forces
OL,13,Fare not for hire, we do not mobilise
OL,14,Fbased on the orders of others," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FIn recent days there has been an
OL,18,Fincrease in Iranian attacks on
OL,19,FKurdistan, mostly targeted at US and
OL,20,Fcoalition facilities.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
