OL,3,CKurds 'should not be treated as US
OL,4,Ccontractors' amid Iran war
OL,6,FBritish forces shot down two drones
OL,7,Fover a site they share with the
OL,8,FAmericans in Erbil, and several US
OL,9,Fsoldiers were injured in the attack.
OL,11,FThe following day a French solider was
OL,12,Fkilled in a strike at a separate base,
OL,13,Fwhere they had been helping to train
OL,14,FKurdish forces in the fight against
OL,15,Fterrorism.
OL,17,FWhile we were filming at the Kurdish
OL,18,Fbase there were several explosions
OL,19,Ffrom attempted airstrikes in the area,
OL,20,Fand we also watched Iranian missiles
OL,21,Ffly over our heads towards Israel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
