CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773529872
OL,3,CKurds 'should not be treated as US
OL,4,Ccontractors' amid Iran war
OL,6,FWe saw first-hand how the Kurds are
OL,7,Fvery much caught in the crosshairs.
OL,9,FThe Kurdistan Region is squeezed
OL,10,Fbetween Iran and Iran-backed militias
OL,11,Fin Iraq, putting people at risk of
OL,12,FIranian retaliation.
OL,14,FThe troops we spoke to said for now
OL,15,Fthey are taking a defensive stance,
OL,16,Fbut if they continue to come under
OL,17,Fattack, or feel the momentum is there,
OL,18,Fthey would be force to go on the
OL,19,Foffensive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773529872
OL,3,CKurds 'should not be treated as US
OL,4,Ccontractors' amid Iran war
OL,6,FMr Ameen insists there are currently
OL,7,Fno plans to get involved in what he
OL,8,Fbelieves could become a protracted war.
OL,10,FHe said: "This situation will not end
OL,11,Feasily. I believe that the US
OL,12,Fgovernment has become involved in a
OL,13,Fconflict from which it cannot easily
OL,14,Fwithdraw.
OL,16,F"Furthermore, I believe the Iranian
OL,17,Fgovernment has unjustifiably made many
OL,18,Fenemies for itself."
OL,26,@rD@JOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
