OL,3,CKurds 'should not be treated as US
OL,4,Ccontractors' amid Iran war
OL,6,FOn the edge of Erbil there is a
OL,7,Fmonument to the 2003 Iraq war, and the
OL,8,Ffall of Saddam Hussein.
OL,10,FIt is a reminder of the historic
OL,11,Fsacrifices Kurds have made for their
OL,12,Fautonomy and people here are worried
OL,13,Fthat this wider war will undo their
OL,14,Fregion's hard-won gains
OL,16,FThey would not mourn the demise of the
OL,17,FIslamic republic, but know only too
OL,18,Fwell, the cost of bringing down a
OL,19,Fregime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
